No. 09-1196. Eleanor Capogrosso, Petitioner v. New York State Commission on Judicial Conduct, et al. 560 U.S. 949, 130 S. Ct. 3360,

176 L. Ed. 2d 1263,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4421. June 1, 2010.

Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.

Justice So-tomayor took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 352 Fed. Appx. 456.
